---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn about Building Products Info — an independent resource providing detailed product information for the UK building and trade industry."
>
  <div class="container static-page">
    <h1>About Building Products Info</h1>

    <p>
      Building Products Info is an independent product information resource for the UK building
      and trade industry. We research and present detailed product data to help professionals
      and serious DIYers make informed purchasing decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Do</h2>
    <p>
      We compile comprehensive product information across all major building and trade categories —
      from hand tools and power tools to plumbing supplies, electrical components, building
      materials, and more. Each product listing includes detailed specifications, key features,
      and relevant information to help you understand what you're buying.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Independent:</strong> We are not owned by any manufacturer, retailer, or trade body.</li>
      <li><strong>Comprehensive:</strong> We cover products across 8 major trade categories.</li>
      <li><strong>Detailed:</strong> Every product listing includes full specifications and key feature breakdowns.</li>
      <li><strong>Practical:</strong> Our buying guides are written for real-world trade and DIY scenarios.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Some of the links on this site are affiliate links. This means if you click through and
      make a purchase, we may receive a small commission at no additional cost to you. This helps
      us keep the site running and continue producing independent product information. For full
      details, see our <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/">Affiliate Disclosure</a> page.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions, suggestions, or would like to submit a product for inclusion,
      please get in touch at <strong>info@buildingproductsinfo.co.uk</strong>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
